# .gitignore — combined ignore rules for firmware/ and android/
#
# Both components share this single root-level file.
# Add firmware rules under the ESP-IDF section, Android rules under the Android section.
#
# Intentionally committed (not ignored) — may look surprising:
#   firmware/sdkconfig          pinned build config for reproducible builds across machines
#   firmware/dependencies.lock  pinned cJSON component version
#
# Security — never remove these lines:
#   *.keystore / *.jks          Android signing keys — must never be committed
#   google-services.json        Firebase credentials — not used yet but pre-emptively ignored
#   local.properties            Android Studio local SDK path — machine-specific, not portable
#
# Related:
#   notes/repo-map.md           full map of what is and isn't in the repo

# ESP-IDF / firmware
build/
managed_components/
.claude/
*.bin
*.elf
*.map

# Android
*.apk
*.ap_
*.aab
*.dex
*.class
bin/
gen/
out/
.gradle/
local.properties
*.iml
.idea/
.navigation/
captures/
.externalNativeBuild/
.cxx/
*.jks
*.keystore
google-services.json
*.hprof
